high_descs: Back away slightly and face the blue rubbish bin to the left of the drawers.
Pick up the white spray bottle from the rubbish bin.
Turn around and move to the left side of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on top of the left side of the toilet cistern.
Move to the door then turn right and move to the blue rubbish bin.
Pick up the white spray bottle from the rubbish bin.
Turn around and move to the left side of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle between the spray bottle and the soap dispenser on top of the toilet cistern.
anns.task_desc: Place two spray bottles on the toilet cistern.

high_descs: Look down at the trash can.
Pick up one of the spray bottles out of the trash can.
Turn right and walk forward at the sink then turn right again. Walk forward then turn right again to face the toilet.
Place spray bottle on the back end of the toilet seat.
Turn right and walk forward then turn left at the cabinets. Go forward then make a right to face the trash can again.
Pick up the other spray bottle from the trash can.
Turn right and walk forward at the sink then turn right again. Walk forward then turn right again to face the toilet.
Place spray bottle on the back end of the toilet seat.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to the back end of a toilet.

high_descs: Look down at the trash can
Grab the spray bottle out of the trash can
Turn around and go to the left side of the toilet
Put the bottle on the top of the toilet
Turn right and go to the trash can
Grab the spray bottle out of the trash can
Turn around and go to the left side of the toilet
Put the spray bottle on the top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Putting two spray bottles on top of a toilet
